* Iron Raptor glared at the Ark from where she stood, that blast had worried 
her but when Iris had said that she was looking after it she calmed down a 
little. She looked around at the destruction and sighed, THIS...was war!
Iron Raptor turned and looked at the fuzor now standing beside her, it 
wasn't the best of times to meet a new face but they needed all of the 
troops they could get!
She then turned her head back towards the Ark...*

" You can tag along for as long as you like, and 'yes', I am a Maximal.
That loud boom that you had heard only minuets before was the Predacons 
getting the better of us, an explosion that they had set off inside of the 
ship."

* Iron Raptor growled deeply, it had been a long day...and it was bound to 
get longer!*
